{
  "texts": [
    "Besides that, their analysis revealed seven major types of deep learning architectures that have been employed for software engineering tasks, including RNNs, encoder-decoder models, CNNs, FNNs, AutoEncoders, Siamese neural networks, and highly tailored architectures.",
    "Our survey differs from Watson et al. [24] in that Watson et al.",
    "took software engineering as a whole to discuss the advances and challenges in applying deep learning techniques to software engineering.",
    "In contrast, we discuss the advances and challenges for each software engineering task concerning how deep learning techniques could be employed to resolve the given software engineering task.The survey conducted by Niu et al. [25] reviews pre-trained models used in software engineering.",
    "In total, they identified and analyzed 20 pre-trained models developed for software engineering tasks."
  ]
}